To build these utilities, use
make utility_name

e.g. make make_torrent for creating torrent file.

All utilities are self explanatory and needs arguments while running.

Utility name		Purpose
make_torrent		Create .torrent file from given input file or directory
dump_torrent		Show information about the torrent like trackers, file present etc.
simple_client		Simple client to download torrent file. 
client_test		Sophisticated client which shows several information during torrent downloading
etc.

The main prerequistic to build utilities is the libtorrent-rasterbar installed. If libtorrent-rasterbar has been built but not installed use the make file present in the example/ folder to build utilities.
